{
  "stem": "18778.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You remember this little boy, this tow-haired little kid that you grew up with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In this case, it was my father's partner's son.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And you know, being an only child, I was so much at their house, 'cause they had four children and each child had friends over all the time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I loved being over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were together almost every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we traveled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And first of all, we saw people we knew in the hotel already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first event was a get-- a get-together to meet each other in the town hall in Monchengladbach.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This time Rheydt is no longer a separate community, but Monchengladbach has three towns combined into one municipality now, the town where my mother was, Odenkirchen, Rheydt, and Monchengladbach.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- some of the assemblies took place in Monchengladbach and some of them took place in Rheydt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We also had a team along from the television show, because somebody was related to somebody who was connected with that show.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they filmed the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My daughter also filmed the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think her-- her film is just as good as the other one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we were in a big hall with some familiar faces, with some faintly familiar faces.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somebody pointed out a portly man to me with glasses and gray hair and a mustache and he wore a hat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, there he is-- his sisters to be exact.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was this little tow-haired kid 50 years later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Culture shock.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only that, I fell around his neck and kissed him and hugged him and he looked at me like, who's this crazy woman?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he's very orthodox and this was strictly taboo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is his name, Liesl?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
